 Governor Gboyega Oyetola of Osun made the remarks during the state’s International Fashion Week in Osogbo. The spokesperson to the governor, Ismail Omipidan, said that the governor’s directive would take effect from August 27. The governor maintained the initiative was part of efforts to preserve and promote the production of Adire Osun as well as bolster the image of Osun as a culturally correct and indigenous product inclined state. <img class="alignnone  wp-image-10394 lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/l57LFPo.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i0.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Screenshot-2021-05-05-at-1.47.18-AM.png?resize=132,41&amp;ssl=1" alt="EBITU | #EbituBlog" width="132" height="41" data-recalc-dims="1"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-10394 lazyload jetpack-lazy-image" src="https://i1.wp.com/mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/l57LFPo.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i0.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Screenshot-2021-05-05-at-1.47.18-AM.png?resize=132%2C41&#038;ssl=1" alt="EBITU | #EbituBlog" width="132" height="41" data-recalc-dims="1" data-lazy-src="https://i1.wp.com/mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/l57LFPo.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i0.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Screenshot-2021-05-05-at-1.47.18-AM.png?resize=132%2C41&amp;is-pending-load=1#038;ssl=1" srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7"><noscript><img class="alignnone  wp-image-10394 lazyload" src="https://i1.wp.com/mlpthjcvvzze.i.optimole.com/l57LFPo.2zvi~5f0f9/w:auto/h:auto/q:90/https://i0.wp.com/ebitu.net/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/Screenshot-2021-05-05-at-1.47.18-AM.png?resize=132%2C41&#038;ssl=1" alt="EBITU | #EbituBlog" width="132" height="41" data-recalc-dims="1" data-recalc-dims="1"> The post Public and civil servants to wear uniform in Osun State — Gov Oyetola appeared first on E B I T U™.